snippet.title: Bramble: The Mountain King - Official Gameplay Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Get your first look at gameplay from Bramble: The Mountain King, the Nordic fairy tale-inspired platformer/adventure game following a young boy and a perilous journey to save his sister. It will be available on Steam next year. Wishlist it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1623940/Bramble_The_Mountain_King/

#IGN #Gaming
